The Text provides the following key information:

1. The TLC (Tutoring Learning Centre) is open for both in-person and online tutoring.
2. Users can learn how to log in using their GBC (George Brown College) credentials.
3. There are handouts and resources available for math coursework.
4. Users can sign up to receive information about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more.
5. Contact details for the TLC: phone number 416-415-2000, TTY number 1-877-515-5559, email ask.george@georgebrown.ca.
6. Social Media Hub is available to visit.
7. The information on the website is subject to change without notice.
8. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
